{"tid":1491944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"打開民意戰嘅手足入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T15:28:20.000Z","uid":297088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b41cbdb0c0a48cde568de884a5561661da7ce0a9","tid":1491944,"uid":297088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"其實諗諗下有冇得搞下一個活動 係光顧返因為受示威活動影響嘅舖頭 純粹可能每個星期六或者日去受影響嘅區消費 食野買野有好 （當然都係唔幫襯奶共嘅舖頭） <br />\n最緊要係有Gear嘅照帶 係話比佢地知我地示威唔係真係有心想搞到佢地 係真係政府迫我地咁 <br />\n我諗每個區有一千人每星期一日去一區都可以幫到d商户 希望繼續贏下民意 <br />\n<br />\n加上呢個活動難度唔高 都係叫大家去嗰到食野買野 好多手足雖然出唔到力 但係可以出錢<br />\n<br />\n各有各做 兄弟爬山<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"7802901fc9607f6cd2cc2aba07d2aab022ad87b5","tid":1491944,"uid":297088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"*又"},{"pid":"ab0f9750529097420c2bb2834335a8fb4ee7bfe5","tid":1491944,"uid":297088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c21cf34f6723b9da0536897e22fa19a8687939d","tid":1491944,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0y2D12U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0y2D12U.jpg&h=c7bab806&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pYuV4gf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpYuV4gf.jpg&h=52b2bc94&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}